			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Start game as DU\r\n2) Go to Bhaal Temple\r\n3) Talk to Orin by getting spotted.\r\n4) Make sure abductee isn't killed in dialog with skillchecks.\r\n5) Defeat Orin.\r\n6) PostBattleDarkUrge should trigger.\r\n7) Resist Bhaal when he offers DU to be chosen one.\r\n8) DU dies, Withers appears and resurrects everyone.\r\n9) Abductee would also be awakened from the altar (if they survived the battle).\r\n10) Talk to Abductee."
				},
