				"speakerSlotDescription": [
					{}
				],
				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "After the companion or Yenna, survives the battle with Orin. They would leave the party as a temporary follower and take some time to recover from their ordeal before returning to camp.In Yenna's case, she will reappear after hiding somewhere safe during the combat.\r\n\r\nPlayers can talk to them briefly before they return to camp where the companion/Yenna will also disappear from the temple back to camp.\r\n"
				}
			}
